## Redis Caching Pattern (MVP)

```python
import redis.asyncio as aioredis
import json

redis_client = aioredis.from_url(settings.redis_url)

async def get_nearby_stores(lat: float, lng: float) -> list[dict]:
    cache_key = f"stores:{lat:.3f}:{lng:.3f}"

    # Check cache first
    cached = await redis_client.get(cache_key)
    if cached:
        return json.loads(cached)

    # Fetch from Google Places API
    stores = await _fetch_from_google_places(lat, lng)

    # Cache for 10 minutes
    await redis_client.setex(cache_key, 600, json.dumps(stores))
    return stores
```

Cache TTLs:
| Data | TTL |
|---|---|
| Nearby stores (Google Places) | 10 min |
| Kroger product availability | 5 min |
| Recipe ingredient list | 60 min |
| AI-generated ingredient extraction | 24 h |

