## Security (MVP minimum)

- `Settings()` crashes at startup if any required env var is missing
- CORS configured in `main.py` — whitelist explicit origins, not `*` in production
- No secrets in source code or logs
- `POST`/`PUT`/`DELETE` endpoints require auth header (even if stub for MVP)

> **Post-MVP hardening:** Rate limiting · SQL injection audit · `sanitize-html` on AI output · JWT auth with Supabase Auth

---

## MVP Checklist

- [ ] `uvicorn app.main:app --reload` starts with zero errors
- [ ] No business logic or DB queries in routers
- [ ] All handlers are `async def`
- [ ] `httpx` used for external HTTP — never `requests`
- [ ] Independent async calls use `asyncio.gather()`
- [ ] AI JSON output wrapped in `try/except json.loads()`
- [ ] New env vars added to `Settings` class in `config.py`
- [ ] No secrets hardcoded or logged

> **Post-MVP:** Repository layer · Circuit breakers (tenacity) · AI self-correction retry loop · Full auth middleware
